main event: On July 7, 1966, a UFO was sighted in Conroe, Texas, where witnesses observed a single object for approximately 5-10 minutes.
interesting points: The object displayed blinking lights that varied in intensity and color, The phenomenon appeared to execute maneuvers and changes in speed and direction, The object was described as being around 50 to 60 feet in diameter and hovered at an estimated elevation of 3,000 to 5,000 feet, Multiple witnesses observed the object, and a report indicated a low humming sound associated with it, The observation was part of a systematic study by Project Blue Book.
sighted object: One unidentified flying object with blinking lights
witness description: Witnesses described seeing a bright light that changed in intensity and color, as well as hearing a low hum.
